high_descs: Turn left and walk past the refrigerator, stop at the counter on the right with the coffee maker on it.
Open the cupboard above the counter and take out the mug.
Turn around and walk towards the sink.
Place the mug in the sink and turn on the water.
Take the mug and walk to the counter behind you with the coffee maker on it.
Place the mug on the drip tray of the coffee maker under the brewer.
anns.task_desc: Take the mug from the cupboard and put it on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the end of the counters on your right, then look up at the cabinet on the right.
Grab a mug from the cabinet.
Turn right, then turn right at the fridge to reach the sink.
Wash the mug in the sink.
Turn around and walk back to the counter under the cabinet where you grabbed the mug.
Place the mug inside of the coffee machine on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed mug in a coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around go straight back and then turn right to find the coffee maker.
Look up, and take out a cup from the cabinet and shut the door.
Take the cup and turn around to go straight back and find the sink.
Place the cup in the sink, turn the water on and then off. Pick up the cup.
Take the cup and turn around. Go straight to the other side, and left to find the coffee maker.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a cup and place it on the coffee maker.
